short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Instantly fill lineup for DraftKings contests.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Even if you play fantasy sports regularly, and know your way around DraftKings' interface, entering a lineup can be time consuming especially if you're entering multiple lineups. Luckily for you, our free Chrome extension can solve this problem effectively cutting down the time to select all the players in your lineup.
